definitions.definition: Chiefly preceded by the : something which is below the limen or threshold of conscious perception .
Chiefly preceded by the : the subconscious ( dated ) or unconscious self .
An advertisement , a message , etc., which is conveyed in a manner that a person is unaware of being influenced by it.

main_definition: ( physiology ) Chiefly preceded by the : something which is below the limen or threshold of conscious perception . [from late 19th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( psychology ) Chiefly preceded by the : the subconscious ( dated ) or unconscious self . [from late 19th c.]
( by extension ) An advertisement , a message , etc., which is conveyed in a manner that a person is unaware of being influenced by it. [from mid 20th c.]
